text: Hendrikus "Driekske" van Bussel (18 November 1868 - 27 April 1951) was an archer from the Netherlands. Van Bussel competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Driekske van Bussel == References == Category:1868 births Category:1951 deaths Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
